<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA27">
<l>aravamoṉ ṟākattu nīnayantu pūṇēl</l>
<l>paravit toḻutirantōm paṉṉāṇ - muraṇaḻiya</l>
<l>voṉṉātār mūveyilu mōrampā leytāṉē</l>
<l>poṉṉāra maṟṟoṉṟu pūṇ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Don’t you lovingly wear a snake on [your] chest?</l>
<l>Man days we have lauded, worshipped, begged,</l>
<l>you who shot the three enemies’ forts with a single arrow,</l>
<l>for another ornament, a golden garland.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
